# NETWORK::NETWORK_CLAN_SERVICE_IS_VALID

## Returns
* **BOOL**

## Notes
<!-- AUTOGENERATED: Remove this line before editing -->
Returns true if the clan service is a ready.
Make sure the service is available before operations.
